--- 
title: Blog
layout: blogList.njk
description: These are all the blog posts I've written since I started web development back in 2017.
---

<div class="wrapper blog-list-wrapper">
  <h1 class="title blog-list-title">Blog</h1>
  <p class="blog-introduction">
      These are all the blog posts I've written since I started web development back in 2017. There are currently <strong>{{ collections.posts.length }}</strong>. Have a browse, see <a class="all-tags-link" href="/tags">all tags</a> here, and add <span class="rss-feed-text">
      <a class="rss-feed-link" href="/rss.xml">my RSS feed</a>!<img src="/img/rss-feed-icon.svg" alt="rss feed icon"/></span>
  </p>
  <ul class="blog-list">
    {% for p in collections.posts | reverse %}
      <li>
        <a class="blog-list-post-title" href="{{ p.url }}" aria-label="A blog post - {{ p.data.title }}">{{ p.data.title }}</a>
        <p class="blog-list-date">{{ p.data.date | readableBlogListDate }}</p>
        {% if p.data.excerpt %}
          <p class="blog-list-excerpt">{{ p.data.excerpt | toHTML | safe }}â€¦</p>
        {% else %}
          <p class="blog-list-excerpt">{{ p.templateContent | getExcerpt }}</p>
        {% endif %}
        <p class="tags blog-list-tags">
          {% for tag in p.data.tags %}
            {%- if collections.tagList.indexOf(tag) != -1 -%}
              {% set tagUrl %}/tags/{{ tag }}/{%endset %}
              <a href="{{ tagUrl | url }}" aria-label="{{ tag }} tag">{{ tag }}</a>
            {%- endif -%}
          {% endfor %}
        </p>
      </li>
    {% endfor %}
  </ul>
</div>